sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2KFy8P7L5Q7LibvWTvnNLyFXnVrNJibRGpKwicia02tbt9P64pR4IRPcG99WYGribBxGwMmoZT7KsJ60A/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">不仅Stable Video立马上线了公测，</span><span style="font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">而且Pika也随即拿出了给视频对口型的Lip Sync，以及可以根据内容自动生成声音的<span style="text-wrap: wrap;">音效生成功能。</span></span></p><p><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3365914978641526784" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2KFy8P7L5Q7LibvWTvnNLyFap5zH5zEogP5CVRib62Lecyic2I8WWKRmoDFU6Nz5xbwiaD0KkdSOLVsw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1280" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3365914978641526784"></iframe></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">LTX Studio则另辟蹊径，上线了电影制作平台，把视频生成、编辑、剪辑、旁白一条龙全包了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="307" data-backw="562" data-height="350" data-imgfileid="504970380" data-ratio="0.546875" data-type="gif" data-w="640" data-width="640" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2KFy8P7L5Q7LibvWTvnNLyF5CcP08ibYXCVynF4CksZYO4dGKdicRGDIiavibpVRuNR9ggtj7UQEADvjw/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: